{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":". Keep this property set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"syntax":null,"code":["performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case","involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)scalesWithViewingDistance","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L180","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"}},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","kind":"symbol","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"tilted map."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"MLNAnnotation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"title":"MLNAnnotationImage"}}}